title: Ringtones 1.0 [K]rack'd, Ring tones from your iTunes lib
description:
Official Web Site: <a href=" http://blog.thelittleappfactory.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://blog.thelittleappfactory.com/</a>

Ringtones creates unlimited iPhone ringtones from your iTunes music. When launched, it displays music in your iTunes library. Select a song, and then select part of the song that you wish to be repetitive as a ring tone.

System Requirements:

OS version: 10.5 and later
